&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Logistics Coordinator to manage the movement of robots, spare parts, data collection equipment, and other materials between Figure HQ, customer sites, and field deployments. This role will be the central point of coordination for all field logistics working closely with our deployment, data collection, service, manufacturing and manufacturing teams to ensure all of our offsite operations run smoothly.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
