&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re seeking a Deployment Staging Specialist to support our offsite data collection operations. This hands-on role involves traveling to collection homes across the country to set up realistic environments — arranging furniture, props, and scene configurations—that enable high-quality data capture for training our humanoid robots.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your work directly impacts Figure&#39;s path to generalized humanoids by ensuring our robots learn from diverse, well-constructed real-world scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel to offsite data collection locations (75%+ travel required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up and configure collection home environments, including furniture arrangement, prop placement, and scene staging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure environments meet specifications for optimal data collection quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with the data collection team to understand scene requirements and timelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Load, unload, and transport equipment, furniture, and props to collection sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain inventory of props and equipment; report damage or replacement needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot on-site issues and adapt setups as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document site configurations and capture photos for reference&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure collection spaces are safe and compliant with operational standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of experience in set design, staging, event setup, warehouse operations, or similar hands-on role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to travel 75% or more, including extended stays at remote locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with physical work: lifting 30+ lbs regularly, moving furniture, standing for extended periods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid driver&#39;s license and clean driving record - Comfortable driving a van&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and ability to follow setup specifications precisely&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter who can work independently with minimal supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communication skills and ability to coordinate with remote teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility to adapt to changing schedules and site conditions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to pass a background check&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with smart home devices or consumer electronics setup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with inventory management or logistics&lt;/li&gt;
