&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an &lt;strong&gt;Electrical Rework Technician&lt;/strong&gt; to own PCBA rework, micro-soldering, and board-level repair across Figure’s humanoid robot hardware. This role is focused on high-quality workmanship, precision rework, and fast turnaround of complex electronics during development, validation, and early production.&lt;/p&gt;
