&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of professional experience in electronics soldering and PCBA rework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive hands-on experience with fine-pitch and high-density PCBAs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven expertise in micro-soldering under microscope&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of PCB construction, component packages, and thermal behavior&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to consistently produce clean, reliable, and inspectable rework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High attention to detail and pride in workmanship&lt;/li&gt;
