&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a skilled &lt;strong&gt;Gear Machinist &lt;/strong&gt;to join our machine shop. In this role, you will work closely with engineering and production teams to design, produce, and inspect precision gears and gear systems that are critical to our development.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
