&lt;li&gt;Document and track workflow, inspection results, and non-conformances&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform preventative maintenance and repair on machines and equipment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
