&lt;li&gt;Proficient in gear hobbing processes, tooling selection, and setup&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with gear skiving for internal profiles and splines&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of gear geometry, tolerances, and quality standards&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to read and interpret engineering drawings, GD&amp;amp;T, and gear specifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
